T02D3618:239b-1: bista ra dzam bha la s'a dha nam /
T02D3618:239b-3: dzam bha la'i sgrub thabs rgyas pa /
T02D3618:239b-4: dpal ldan dzam bha la la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3618:239b-5: stong pa nyid bsgoms pa'i rjes su cung zad dmar
T02D3618:239b-6: ba'i zla ba'i dkyil 'khor la gnod sbyin gyi shing
T02D3618:239b-7: rta zur gsum padma 'dab ma brgyad pa'i rnam pa'o
T02D3618:239b-8: // de'i dbus su bam yig las nor rgyun ma
T02D3618:239b-9: sku mdog ser mo phyag na 'bras kyi snye ma
T02D3618:239b-11: rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
T02D3618:240a-0: gnod sbyin mo brgyad kyis yongs su bskor ba @240a * //
T02D3618:240a-9: chu shel ma rnams kyis yongs su bskor ba /
T02D3618:240a-10: lha mo chen mo de'i bha ga'i dbus su dzam
T02D3618:240a-11: yig las skyes pa'i dzam bha la nor rgyun ma
T02D3618:240a-12: la 'khyud pa / byang chub kyi sems nges par
T02D3618:240a-13: sbyor bas rin po che phyag na yang dag par
T02D3618:240a-14: bstod pa gsal bar bsgom par bya'o //
T02D3618:240a-15: 'bab pa'i dus su bcom ldan 'das kyi shar phyogs su nor bu bzang po sku mdog sngon po'o //
T02D3618:240a-16: lho phyogs su gang ba bzang po ser po'o //
T02D3618:240a-17: nub phyogs su rnam thos sras dmar po'o //
T02D3618:240a-18: byang phyogs su gnod sbyin dmar po'o //
T02D3618:240a-19: me dang bden bral dang rlung dang /
T02D3618:240a-20: dbang ldan gyi mtshams su mu khendra sngon po dang ki li mi li dang /
T02D3618:240a-21: ki li mi li chen po dang /
T02D3618:240a-22: zhal gyi dbang po sku mdog dmar po dang /
T02D3618:240a-23: spyod pa'i dbang po sku mdog ljang gu ste /
T02D3618:240a-24: gser gyi zur phud lnga pa /
T02D3618:240a-25: phyag g-yas na b'i dza p'u ra ka dang /
T02D3618:240a-26: g-yon na rin po che 'bar ba 'bo bzhin pa'i sre mong bsnams pa /
T02D3618:240a-27: de bzhin gshegs pa lnga 'phro ba /
T02D3618:240a-28: padma can dang dung can gyi gter chen po'i mgo
T02D3618:240a-29: bor rin po che'i char 'bebs bzhin pa rang gi
T02D3618:240a-30: khang pa'i gnas kyi phyogs gcig tu bsam par bya'o
T02D3618:240a-31: // mgon po dzam bha la sku mdog ser po autpa la sngon po'i phreng ba bsnams pa /
T02D3618:240a-32: de thams cad kyang gnod sbyin mo brgyad kyi bha ga'i dbus su gnas pa /
T02D3618:240a-33: rin po che'i char 'bebs bzhin pa /
T02D3618:240a-34: dzam bha la dang 'dra ba bsgom par bya'o //
T02D3618:240a-35: shar sgor nor sbyin dang nor sbyin chen po /
T02D3618:240a-36: lho sgor gnod sbyin dang gnod sbyin chen po dang /
T02D3618:240a-37: nub sgor ki li mi li dang /
T02D3618:240a-38: ki li mi li chen po'o //
T02D3618:240a-39: byang sgor gang ba dang gang ba bzang po chen po ste /
T02D3618:240a-40: de thams cad kyang gcer bu 'bras bu 'phyang ba /
T02D3618:240a-41: lto ba 'phyang zhing rin po che'i char 'bebs pa'o //
T02D3618:240a-42: de nas spyi bor nor bu bzang po /
T02D3618:240a-43: mig gnyis la rnam thos sras /
T02D3618:240a-45: nu ma'i bar du gang ba bzang po /
T02D3618:240a-47: brla dag la ki li mi li dang /
T02D3618:240a-48: ki li mi li chen mo /
T02D3618:240b-0: rkang pa dag la tsi pi kundra li'o zhes pa'i lha rnams @240b bkod la /
T02D3618:240b-1: yi ge rnams dgod par bya'o //
T02D3618:240b-4: tslum ni rna ba dag la'o //
T02D3618:240b-5: mgo bo'i rgyab tu sv'a h'a'o //
T02D3618:240b-7: lag pa'i dbus su slum mo //
T02D3618:240b-8: song mo thams cad la aom dzam bha la dza lendra ye sv'a h'a /
T02D3618:240b-9: aom dzlum tslum sv'a h'a zhes pa'i sngags so //
T02D3618:240b-10: de bzhin du mdzub mo la nor bu bzang po'o //
T02D3618:240b-11: gung mo la gang bzang po'o //
T02D3618:240b-12: ming med la nor sbyin no /
T02D3618:240b-13: mthe'u chung la rnam thos sras so //
T02D3618:240b-14: tsi pi kundra li ni mtheb chen la'o //
T02D3618:240b-15: mkhrig mtshams su ki li mi li na'o //
T02D3618:240b-16: yi ga rnams lag pa la bkod nas /
T02D3618:240b-17: snga bar rdo rje'i chu la sogs pa'i bdud rtsi lnga ste /
T02D3618:240b-18: de'i ngo bo ma yin pa yang rdo rje'i chu tsam yang bsres te khyor bas 'thung nas /
T02D3618:240b-19: lag pas khyor ba brgya rtsa brgyad dbul bar bya'o //
T02D3618:240b-20: / thun mtshams gsum gyis yun ring bar 'grub par 'gyur ro //
T02D3618:240b-21: aom dzlum tslum slum sam zhes brjod nas chu khyor bas sbyin par bya'o //
T02D3618:240b-22: gal te de bzhin byas bas ma grub na /
T02D3618:240b-23: dpal rdo rje h'um mdzad kyi skur bdag nyid bsgoms nas /
T02D3618:240b-24: dzam bha la'i sku gzugs la dug dang ske tshe
T02D3618:240b-25: dang tshva dang myos byed kyi lo ma'i khu ba
T02D3618:240b-26: dang dur khrod kyi sol bas byugs te /
T02D3618:240b-27: dur khrod kyi me la khros pas bdugs na /
